N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 42.4 - Approval of brake fluids

State Regulations

It is not necessary to submit samples or secure formal
approval of any brake fluid. Any brake fluids may be used provided they conform
to the provisions of this Part and all brake fluids which conform to this Part
are hereby approved. Notes
